{"tid":2018510,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［蘋果好波！］未開考前教育局官員已經睇過份卷！點解等考完先出嚟鬧？？","createTime":"2020-05-15T16:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T20:12:40.000Z","uid":211994,"like":1296,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":132,"replies":[{"pid":"0bac39adfae275123fd89c3dafb9ac2d44a11eed","tid":2018510,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200515&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60943186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200515%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60943186&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=d09cfd3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200515%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60943186&h=2cdd5d4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200515&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60943186</a><br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試歷史科有關中國和日本的試題引起軒然大波，教育局史無前例公開譴責試題，更將派員到考試及評核局「了解機制」。《蘋果》獲悉，考評局近年在教育局壓力下，各科的審題委員會都需要「邀請」教育局人員加入，今次引起爭議的歷史科試卷亦不例外，其審題委員會有一名教育局課程發展處官員參與，早於歷史科開考前已對有關的出題策略和內容知情"},{"pid":"443326e988d20fff2bb1bd117de87c594e6d4a02","tid":2018510,"uid":211994,"like":488,"dislike":0,"score":488,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"做鳩考評局同時可以維穩，一石二鳥<br />\n可惜香港有蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e83a8857649956870b8a574d474ce5ffa8ccd2","tid":2018510,"uid":211994,"like":250,"dislike":0,"score":250,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:05:27.000Z","msg":"楊焗腸你啲仔女喺邊度讀書㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81209178031af8f62207fa53f7db36be408780b","tid":2018510,"uid":103618,"like":168,"dislike":0,"score":168,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"美國有蘋果 香港都有蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3308554c03cc831d019348e95a8511b36264ae41","tid":2018510,"uid":211994,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"cit